resources.string:
You have periodic payment subscription(monthly,yearly etc..), you can enjoy all the Threads downloader Premium privileges during this subscription period. 

The subscription will automatically renew at the trial ends(or the current subscription period ends), unless you cancel your subscription at least 24 hours before the renewal date. 

You can go to the account page of Google Play to manage or cancel the subscription, there is no charge for cancellation during the trial period.
